msgctxt "sn23.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 2. Dutiyamāravagga → dutiyavaggo (s1-3) | dutiyo vaggo (pts1) | dutiyavagga (c1, c2)
msgctxt "sn23.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyamāravagga "
msgstr "2. About Māra (2nd) "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Mārasutta "
msgstr "11. About Māra "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.195, sc1
msgctxt "sn23.11:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.11:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā rādho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, Venerable Rādha said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.11:1.3"
msgid "“‘māro, māro’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘Māra’. "

msgctxt "sn23.11:1.4"
msgid "Katamo nu kho, bhante, māro”ti? "
msgstr "How is Māra defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.11:1.5"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, māro, vedanā māro, saññā māro, saṅkhārā māro, viññāṇaṃ māro. "
msgstr "“Rādha, form is Māra, feeling is Māra, perception is Māra, choices are Māra, consciousness is Māra. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.11:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ, rādha, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi nibbindati, saññāyapi nibbindati, saṅkhāresupi nibbindati, viññāṇasmimpi nibbindati. "
msgstr "Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn23.11:1.7"
msgid "Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.11:1.8"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.11:1.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

